snippet.textDisplay:
Hello! Turn to Jesus Christ while there’s still time! Jesus is the way, the truth, and the life no one goes to the Father except through him (John 14:6). None of us are good enough to enter Heaven (Ephesians 2:8), we have all sinned and fallen short of the glory of God (Romans 3:23). Think you’re a good person? Read ( 1 Corinthians 6:9-10, Galatians 5:21, Ephesians 5:5, Revelation 21:8, Mathew 19:17). Jesus also says you must be born again (John 3:3) to see the kingdom. To be changed into a new person in Christ and cleansed from all unrighteousness.

We are all deserving of hell because of our sins against God but the gift of eternal life is only through Jesus Christ (Romans 6:23). Jesus paid the ultimate price the sins of the whole world! Jesus is perfect, he never sinned so that we may be made right with God and adopted by him (2 Corinthians 5:21, Ephesians 1: 4-7). Jesus died on the cross and rose again on the third day defeating death and is now at the right hand of God (Hebrews 10:12). Believe in the gospel of Jesus Christ and repent from your sins (Mark 1:15). God is not willing that anyone should perish but all to come to repentance (2 Peter 3:9). We will all die one day, then the judgement (Hebrews 9:27). Tomorrow is not promised, choose to turn to Jesus now! Life on earth is short but going to hell and dying the second death for rejecting Jesus is forever, an eternity.

God loved the world to send us a savior (John 3:16) but God also has a perfect hatred against sin (Proverbs 6:16-19). Humble yourself and call on the Lord to forgive you of your sins (1 John 5:9). Seek him and you’ll find him(Jeremiah 29:13). Be baptized (Mathew 28:18,Acts 2:38). Live for a greater purpose!
God Bless, Jesus is our hope!❤️
